We offer traditional Cuban cuisine, serving breakfast and lunch!
​
Customers love our food and the quaint atmosphere! Come in for a cup of authentic Cuban coffee and dessert, or stop by for some breakfast to kick off your day.
​
We’ve been serving amazing food in the city of Marathon, great for families, locals, and tourists alike!
